text: TRO or tro may refer to: * Tamils Rehabilitation Organisation * Temporary restraining order * Tro (instrument), Cambodian string instrument * "Tro" (song), 1996, Marie Fredriksson * TRO (gene) (trophinin), a human protein involved in cell adhesion * Taree Airport, IATA code * The Richmond Organization, Inc., music publisher * TRO (company), an architectural firm
